OL,3,CGerry Adams suffers 'last man standing
OL,4,Csyndrome,' former IRA man tells court
OL,6,FGerry Adams "bears both the prize and
OL,7,Fthe burden of being the last prominent
OL,8,FProvisional IRA leader", a former
OL,9,Fmember of the terrorist group has told
OL,10,Fthe High Court in London.
OL,12,FShane Paul O'Doherty, who was jailed
OL,13,Ffor 14 years over an IRA letter bomb
OL,14,Fcampaign in London in the 1970s, gave
OL,15,Fevidence in the civil trial brought
OL,16,Fagainst the former Sinn Fein president
OL,17,Fto say he was a leading member of the
OL,18,FProvisional IRA.
OL,26,@nD@MOUpD@WO]xD@Zrr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
