OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773280992
OL,3,CGerry Adams suffers 'last man standing
OL,4,Csyndrome,' former IRA man tells court
OL,6,FMr Adams denies ever being in the
OL,7,FProvisional IRA and is defending the
OL,8,Fclaim.
OL,10,FIn his witness statement for the
OL,11,Ftrial, Mr O'Doherty said: "All PIRA
OL,12,Fvolunteers who joined the PIRA in the
OL,13,Fearly 1970s and thereafter were
OL,14,Finstructed to lie to everyone about
OL,15,Ftheir PIRA membership ` this meant
OL,16,Flying to their families, whether to
OL,17,Ftheir parents or to their wives and
OL,18,Fchildren."
OL,26,@sD@[OUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
