OL,3,CGerry Adams suffers 'last man standing
OL,4,Csyndrome,' former IRA man tells court
OL,6,FHe added: "No-one took this PIRA
OL,7,Fpolicy to lying to such an absurd
OL,8,Fextreme as Adams."
OL,10,FMr O'Doherty, who has been publicly
OL,11,Fcritical of the IRA following his
OL,12,Fprison sentence, also described Mr
OL,13,FAdams as "suffering from the 'last man
OL,14,Fstanding' syndrome".
OL,26,@nD@KOUpD@RO]uD@JOUvD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
