CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773280992
OL,3,CGerry Adams suffers 'last man standing
OL,4,Csyndrome,' former IRA man tells court
OL,6,FHe said: "By this I mean that since so
OL,7,Fmany prominent PIRA leaders are now
OL,8,Fdead, he alone bears both the prize
OL,9,Fand the burden of being the last
OL,10,Fprominent PIRA leader to bear witness
OL,11,Fto the PIRA's long and horrible
OL,12,Fcampaign of terrorism including some
OL,13,Fof its worst atrocities dating from
OL,14,Fthe early 1970s."
OL,16,FCross-examining, Edward Craven KC, for
OL,17,FMr Adams, said: "You have never met Mr
OL,18,FAdams, you have never spoken to him or
OL,19,Fbeen to a meeting with him.
OL,26,@nD@JOUvD@QO]yD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
