CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773280992
OL,3,CGerry Adams suffers 'last man standing
OL,4,Csyndrome,' former IRA man tells court
OL,6,F"Yesterday was the first time in your
OL,7,Flife you have ever been in the same
OL,8,Froom as him."
OL,10,FMr O'Doherty said: "I have never
OL,11,Fpersonally met him, I would very much
OL,12,Fhave liked to meet him and have
OL,13,Fdiscussions."
OL,15,FHe said later: "I have never spoken to
OL,16,FKing Charles but I know he's the King."
OL,18,FAlso giving evidence was Colonel
OL,19,FRichard Kemp, who served with the
OL,20,FBritish Army in Northern Ireland in
OL,21,Fthe 1980s and 1990s.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@MO]rD@TOUuD@MO]wD@POUxD@gO]
