OL,3,CGerry Adams suffers 'last man standing
OL,4,Csyndrome,' former IRA man tells court
OL,6,FHe also worked for a time as an
OL,7,Fintelligence officer and he told the
OL,8,Fcourt that he had seen information
OL,9,Fshowing Mr Adams to be in the IRA.
OL,11,FCross-examining, James Robottom said:
OL,12,F"You cannot tell this court how
OL,13,Freliable that intelligence was."
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
