OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773280992
OL,3,CGerry Adams suffers 'last man standing
OL,4,Csyndrome,' former IRA man tells court
OL,6,FCol Kemp said: "I cannot give very
OL,7,Fspecific intelligence reports for
OL,8,Freasons that you will understand and
OL,9,Fmy memory, but I do know I saw
OL,10,Fintelligence and was briefed on
OL,11,Fintelligence for a period of around 20
OL,12,Fyears, which made it clear that Mr
OL,13,FAdams was in the IRA.
OL,15,F"I think it is inconceivable that
OL,16,Fintelligence that was not correct
OL,17,Fwould have been reported over that
OL,18,Fperiod of time."
OL,26,@nD@POUwD@AOUzD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
