OL,3,CGerry Adams suffers 'last man standing
OL,4,Csyndrome,' former IRA man tells court
OL,6,FHe added: "I don't remember a piece of
OL,7,Fevidence indicating Mr Adams was in
OL,8,Fthe IRA being withdrawn."
OL,10,FThe trial, before Mr Justice Swift, is
OL,11,Fdue to conclude later in March.
